        <div id="dsq-comment-body-91" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-91" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Silver? Unless we are heading hi-inflation, isn&#8217;t it suspect [bubble]?<br />
Gold? Some argue that it became really expensive vs. housing (and may be bubbly, too).<br />
Housing? (lots of concerns and actual issues here)<br />
Commodities? They sure seem overpriced nowadays&#8230;</p>
<p>Thoughts?</p>
</div>
